### Lister toutes les candidatures
GET http://localhost:8080/api/applications

### Créer une candidature
POST http://localhost:8080/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Capgemini",
  "position": "Développeur Full Stack React Nodejs",
  "status": "APPLIED",
  "appliedAt": "2026-07-06",
  "notes": ""
}

### Voir une candidature par id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/applications/3

### Modifier une candidature
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/applications/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "SQLI",
  "position": "Consultant Fullstack Java/Angular",
  "status": "INTERVIEW",
  "appliedAt": "2026-07-03",
  "notes": "Ils ont répondu ! Entretien prévu."
}

### Supprimer une candidature
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/applications/2

### POST invalide — le videur doit refuser
POST http://localhost:8080/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{"company": "", "position": ""}

### Tenter d'imposer un id — doit être ignoré
POST http://localhost:8080/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{"id": 999, "company": "Devoteam", "position": "Dev Java"}